://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/126362/', '', 'Rabeprazole, Misoprostol, Chondroitin sulfate, Glucosamine, Esomeprazole, Tolazoline, Rabeprazole, Dimethyl sulfoxide', '', 1767369485);
